        <h3>MeU Square <small>- MeU</small></h3>
        <div class="tech-description">
          <img src="img/meu.png" class="pull-left media-object" />
          <div class="media-body">
            <p>
              <em>MeU</em> is an open source <em>wearable LED display</em> that
              can be put into clothing and accessories such as jackets, dresses,
              t-shirts and bags.
            </p>
            <p>
              It can <em>display text, graphics</em> and is <em>controlled by
              smartphone</em> via bluetooth. To change the what’s being
              displayed, just type in the message or choose the image and press
              send.
            </p>
            <p>
              Some of the applications for MeU include <em>bike safety,
              marketing and advertising, fashion and interactive gaming</em>.
            </p>
            <p>
              Learn more at
              <a href="http://www.themeu.net" target="_blank">
                themeu.net
              </a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
